research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Silsbee operates under a mayor-council government type. The city council consists of a mayor and six council members. Information regarding elected officials was primarily sourced from the City of Silsbee's election page, the Texas State Directory Online, and city council meeting minutes from May 2024. While most council members' divisions (At Large or District) were identified, the specific division for Roy Gravis II was not consistently available across all sources, so it is left as an empty array.
